snippet.title: Fae Farm | New consoles announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Faefarm is coming to PlayStation and Xbox October 22! 

Discover the wonderful world of Azoria and build your own magical cozy home on PS5, PS4, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S, and join the thousands of players who already joined us on Nintendo Switch and PC. By yourself or together with up to three friends, dive into endless enchantment as you nurture your land, share bountiful harvests, and embark on magical adventures. 

Both the Standard Edition and Deluxe Edition of Fae Farm will be available at launch, as well as the DLC packs Coasts of Croakia and Skies of Azoria. 🌱

Pre-orders are available now on PlayStation Store.

Join our Discord here: https://discord.gg/faefarm
Join us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FaeFarm/
Join us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/faefarm/
Join us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@faefarm
